(AP Photo/Tony Ding) Posted: Tuesday, October 20, 2015 4:43 pm | Updated: 5:02 pm, Tue Oct 20, 2015. Michigan punter O'Neill doesn't mind his new notoriety Associated Press | 
ANN ARBOR, Mich. (AP) — Blake O'Neill is shrugging off the fact that perhaps millions of people probably didn't know who he was last week. 
"I'm happy to play for Michigan football," the punter said Tuesday night. "You choose to play at the college level, you take the good and the bad."
